  "content": "<p data-pid=\"XW3wrX0m\">前排看了一圈，居然没人提<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lw%25C3%25B3w_School_of_Mathematics\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">利沃夫学派（Lwów School）</a>的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scottish_Book\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">苏格兰书（Scottish Book）</a>与<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scottish_Caf%25C3%25A9\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">酒馆（Scottish Café）</a>（<span class=\"nolink\">Café</span> 也卖酒的！）。</p><p data-pid=\"jRQTvPSZ\">我简单翻译一下 Wikipedia 上的介绍：</p><p data-pid=\"sRr-jhTT\"><span class=\"nolink\">Scottish Café</span>（<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polish_language\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">波兰语</a>：<i>Kawiarnia Szkocka</i>）曾是<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Second_Polish_Republic\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">波兰第二共和国</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lviv\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">利沃夫</a>（今<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ukraine\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">乌克兰</a>利沃夫市）的一家 Café。在 1930 至 1940 年代，<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lw%25C3%25B3w_School_of_Mathematics\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">利沃夫数学学派</a>的数学家们常聚集于此，切磋琢磨<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_problem\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">数学难题</a>，尤其是在<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Functional_analysis\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">泛函分析</a>和<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/General_topology\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">拓扑学</a>领域。</p><p data-pid=\"tYPwr8oz\">据<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanis%25C5%2582aw_Ulam\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">斯坦尼斯瓦夫·乌拉姆</a>回忆，Café 的桌面是<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marble\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">大理石</a>的，所以他们在讨论时，可以用铅笔直接在桌上书写。为了不让这些研究成果付诸东流，也因为对他们直接在桌上乱涂乱画感到恼火，<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stefan_Banach\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">斯特凡·巴拿赫</a>的妻子为数学家们提供了一本大笔记本，用于记录问题和答案，这本笔记最终便以《<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scottish_Book\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">苏格兰书</a>》而闻名。书中收集了已解、未解、甚至可能无解的各种问题，Café 的任何客人都可以借阅。解答任何问题都有奖励，而那些最艰深、最具挑战性的难题，其彩头也尤为贵重（时值<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Great_Depression\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">大萧条</a>末期与<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_War_II\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">二战</a>前夕），例如一瓶上等的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brandy\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">白兰地</a>。</p><p data-pid=\"THVxYUaE\">对于第 153 号问题，<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanis%25C5%2582aw_Mazur\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">斯坦尼斯瓦夫·马祖尔</a>开出的奖品是一只活鹅，该问题后来被公认为与斯特凡·巴拿赫的「<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Approximation_problem\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">基问题</a>」密切相关。此题直到 1972 年才由<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Per_Enflo\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">皮尔·恩弗洛</a>解出，在一个全波兰转播的颁奖仪式上，他领走了这只活鹅作为奖品。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f8038999bc74da6a7d9db604255b2bdf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1600\" data-rawheight=\"1200\" data-original-token=\"v2-f8038999bc74da6a7d9db604255b2bdf\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d144af66f84d72c7a54c851d5e8f538_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1600\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f8038999bc74da6a7d9db604255b2bdf_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1600&#39; height=&#39;1200&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1600\" data-rawheight=\"1200\" data-original-token=\"v2-f8038999bc74da6a7d9db604255b2bdf\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d144af66f84d72c7a54c851d5e8f538_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1600\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f8038999bc74da6a7d9db604255b2bdf_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f8038999bc74da6a7d9db604255b2bdf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><h2>相关文章</h2><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/20351832676\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">非常规小团体的惊人效能</a><p></p>",
